449
00:47:07,533 --> 00:47:10,075
Selamat siang, tuan.

450
00:47:10,783 --> 00:47:11,825
Kau siapa?

451
00:47:13,408 --> 00:47:18,033
Kami makhluk abadi,
jauh-jauh dari Kunlun.

452
00:47:18,033 --> 00:47:20,783
Jadi kami tak punya tanda pengenal.

453
00:47:20,783 --> 00:47:22,533
Tak punya tanda pengenal?

454
00:47:24,991 --> 00:47:26,908
Tapi, kami punya ini.

455
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:33,408
