orang yang tak bersalah!

1213
01:51:25,700 --> 01:51:28,741
Sebagai Pendeta Agung,

1214
01:51:29,116 --> 01:51:32,116
aku punya jantung ajaib bertujuh ruang.

1215
01:51:32,950 --> 01:51:34,908
Begitu dia makan jantung ini,

1216
01:51:35,116 --> 01:51:36,450
siluman mana pun...

1217
01:51:36,866 --> 01:51:40,533
akan berubah ke wujud aslinya.

1218
01:51:40,950 --> 01:51:43,950
Kau mau serahkan jantungmu untuk ini?

1219
01:51:43,950 --> 01:51:45,616
Apa bedanya jantungku...

1220
01:51:45,700 --> 01:51:47,366
dengan keluarga kerajaan...

1221
01:51:48,575 --> 01:51:51,158
dan dinasti kita?

1222
01:51:56,825 --> 01:52:01,616
Tapi jika Su Daji benar siluman rubah,

1223
01:52:01,741 --> 01:52:04,158
Yang Mulia akan lakukan apa?

1224
01:52:07,408 --> 01:52:08,841
Katakan permintaanmu.

1225
01:52:09,533 --> 01:52:10,991
Dia harus dihukum mati.

1226
01:52:12,325 --> 01:52:14,616
Yin Jiao harus diampuni.

1227
01:52:15,366 --> 01:52:17,991
Dan Empat Adipati
harus dinyatakan tak bersalah.

1228
01:52:18,783 --> 01:52:20,741
Atas nama leluhur kita,

1229
01:52:21,366 --> 01:52:24,783
bersumpahlah untuk menepatinya.

1230
01:52:29,616 --> 01:52:31,575
Leluhur akan menjadi saksiku,

1231
01:52:32,741 --> 01:52:34,033
aku bersumpah!

1232
01:52:35,200 --> 01:52:37,866
Paman, jangan!

1233
01:52:56,783 --> 01:52:57,700
Telan itu!

1234
01:53:38,741 --> 01:53:41,116
Siluman rubah,
jangan menyakiti Yang Mulia!

1235
01:53:44,658 --> 01:53:46,033
Siluman rubah sudah menampakkan dirinya.

1236
01:53:46,116 --> 01:53:49,033
Sekarang, Yang Mulia, bunuh dia!

1237
01:53:52,866 --> 01:53:54,700
Atas nama leluhur kita,

1238
01:53:55,116 --> 01:53:58,783
Yin Shou, tunggu apa lagi?

1239
01:54:01,408 --> 01:54:02,366
Leluhur kita?

1240
01:54:07,616 --> 01:54:09,200
Mana para leluhur itu?

1241
01:54:13,075 --> 01:54:15,283
Jika aku panggil mereka,
apa mereka akan jawab?

1242
01:54:17,200 --> 01:54:19,283
Kalian semua bilang
rubah putih ini siluman.

1243
01:54:21,658 --> 01:54:23,783
Malah, dia cantik.

1244
01:54:26,116 --> 01:54:29,408
Cuma dia yang tahu
apa yang sebenarnya aku mau.

1245
01:54:30,700 --> 01:54:32,425
Kau mau jadi...

1246
01:54:32,908 --> 01:54:38,325
Raja Seluruh Dunia.

1247
01:54:50,741 --> 01:54:51,908
Dinasti Shang...

1248
01:54:52,616 --> 01:54:54,116
sudah berakhir.

1249
01:54:57,491 --> 01:54:58,158
Pendeta Agung!

1250
01:54:58,158 --> 01:54:59,825
Dinasti Shang...

1251
01:55:00,450 --> 01:55:03,408
sudah berakhir.

1252
01:55:09,991 --> 01:55:11,575
Paman Agung!

1253
01:55:13,116 --> 01:55:14,366
Dinasti Shang...

1254
01:55:18,283 --> 01:55:20,116
Bawa keluar Pendeta Agung dari sini.

1255
01:55:37,241 --> 01:55:38,533
Bocah pengkhianat,

1256
01:55:39,908 --> 01:55:41,450
menurutmu ini lucu?

1257
01:55:44,241 --> 01:55:47,058
Kurasa Ayah sudah temakan sihir
oleh siluman rubah itu.

1258
01:55:48,533 --> 01:55:51,075
Makanya aku selalu berharap...

1259
01:55:51,533 --> 01:55:53,366
kau akan kembali menjadi...

1260
01:55:53,366 --> 01:55:55,700
seorang ayah...

1261
01:55:55,991 --> 01:55:57,575
yang kuhormati dan kukagumi.

1262
01:55:58,075 --> 01:55:59,700
Aku bodoh sekali.

1263
01:56:02,408 --> 01:56:05,450
Ini ulahmu!

1264
01:56:09,991 --> 01:56:11,866
Kau memberiku kehidupanku.

1265
01:56:13,783 --> 01:56:15,616
Sekarang kau bisa ambil kembali!

1266
01:56:18,325 --> 01:56:19,075
Yin Jiao!

1267
01:56:33,075 --> 01:56:34,158
Pengawal!

1268
01:56:37,991 --> 01:56:39,241
Bawa dia pergi.

1269
01:56:48,533 --> 01:56:50,700
Dia akan dihukum mati
di Gerbang Meridian besok.

1270
01:56:59,366 --> 01:57:01,700
Jangan kira aku tak tahu
apa yang kau rencanakan.

1271
01:57:01,950 --> 01:57:02,908
Aku takkan pernah...

1272
01:57:16,241 --> 01:57:17,700
Dari semua tawanan,

1273
01:57:19,200 --> 01:57:20,700
kaulah kesayanganku,

1274
01:57:22,325 --> 01:57:24,741
karena saat kau tiba di Zhaoge,

1275
01:57:24,741 --> 01:57:26,450
kau bilang padaku,

1276
01:57:26,866 --> 01:57:29,283
kau mau jadi pahlawan.

1277
01:57:31,116 --> 01:57:33,241
Kita ini orang baik,

1278
01:57:34,450 --> 01:57:35,366
jadi,

1279
01:57:37,158 --> 01:57:39,450
satu kesempatan terakhir buatmu.

1280
01:57:39,866 --> 01:57:41,408
Bunuhlah Ji Chang.

1281
01:57:44,575 --> 01:57:45,866
Bunuh,

1282
01:57:47,158 --> 01:57:50,200
kau akan jadi putra dan pewarisku,

1283
01:57:50,950 --> 01:57:53,033
Putra Mahkota Shang.

1284
01:57:54,658 --> 01:57:56,533
Jangan mengecewakanku lagi.

1285
01:58:04,450 --> 01:58:06,783
Aku seorang penjahat.

1286
01:58:07,950 --> 01:58:11,283
Aku tak bisa di ampuni.

1287
01:58:13,866 --> 01:58:16,075
Aku sudah berdosa.

1288
01:58:35,033 --> 01:58:37,825
Kukira aku tak bakalan
melihat sinar matahari lagi,

1289
01:58:38,950 --> 01:58:40,950
tapi kau menyelamatkanku.

1290
01:58:41,783 --> 01:58:43,766
Aku sudah berlatih ribuan tahun...

1291
01:58:44,200 --> 01:58:46,250
agar bisa menjelma jadi manusia...

1292
01:58:46,283 --> 01:58:48,283
dan ikut menikmati dunia.

1293
01:58:50,616 --> 01:58:54,325
Tapi Raja Cheng Tang
mengurungku di Makam Xuanyuan.

1294
01:58:55,908 --> 01:58:57,158
Sudah 500 tahun...

1295
01:58:59,366 --> 01:59:03,283
Hanya keturunannya
yang bisa membuka segel itu.

1296
01:59:04,325 --> 01:59:08,116
Kau menghidupkanku kembali.

1297
01:59:11,741 --> 01:59:13,533
Sebagai balasannya,

1298
01:59:14,325 --> 01:59:16,575
akan kurapalkan
mantra pemindahan roh...

1299
01:59:16,991 --> 01:59:19,241
untuk merasuki tubuh Yin Qi...

1300
01:59:20,283 --> 01:59:22,033
yang akan menuruti keinginanmu,

1301
01:59:23,033 --> 01:59:25,866
dan mendapatkan yang kau mau.

1302
01:59:29,575 --> 01:59:31,366
Akan kujadikan kau abadi,

1303
01:59:33,116 --> 01:59:34,783
seorang Raja yang kekal.

1304
01:59:51,825 --> 01:59:54,158
Seorang rakyat melayani rajanya...

1305
01:59:54,158 --> 01:59:56,250
bagaikan matahari dan bulan di langit.

1306
01:59:56,991 --> 02:00:00,116
Itulah dasar dari sebuah negara.

1307
02:00:01,325 --> 02:00:03,200
Seorang anak melayani Ayahnya...

1308
02:00:03,491 --> 02:00:05,325
seperti para dewa yang ada di langit.

1309
02:00:05,700 --> 02:00:08,158
Itulah pondasi sebuah keluarga.

1310
02:00:09,158 --> 02:00:12,783
Makanya tidak ada dosa
yang lebih besar...

1311
02:00:12,783 --> 02:00:15,450
dari pembunuhan
terhadap ayah dan raja.

1312
02:00:15,783 --> 02:00:17,075
Putra pengkhianat, Yin Jiao,

1313
02:00:17,450 --> 02:00:19,200
sudah melanggar hukum dan etika,

1314
02:00:19,241 --> 02:00:20,825
berniat mau membunuh...

1315
02:00:21,033 --> 02:00:23,366
Ji Chang,

1316
02:00:23,616 --> 02:00:27,741
siapa yang mau ditakdirkan mati
ditangan keturunan kita sendiri?

1317
02:00:27,741 --> 02:00:29,450
Yin Shou!

1318
02:00:30,908 --> 02:00:34,825
Hidup atau mati,
aku akan datang mencarimu!

1319
02:00:34,991 --> 02:00:36,658
Lanjutkan eksekusinya!

1320
02:00:48,533 --> 02:00:51,075
Nezha, Yang Jian, kau dimana?

1321
02:01:03,658 --> 02:01:04,783
Kakak Xiqi,

1322
02:01:05,325 --> 02:01:06,700
selamatkan Yin Jiao!

1323
02:01:17,075 --> 02:01:17,991
Hentikan mereka!

1324
02:01:23,533 --> 02:01:25,825
Beraninya kau menipuku?!

1325
02:01:27,533 --> 02:01:28,950
Lepaskan Yin Jiao,

1326
02:01:28,950 --> 02:01:30,033
atau kubunuh kau.

1327
02:01:32,575 --> 02:01:33,950
Kau tidak akan berani.

1328
02:01:36,241 --> 02:01:37,283
Bunuh dia!

1329
02:01:46,408 --> 02:01:47,158
Kawan,

1330
02:01:47,533 --> 02:01:48,575
aku akan mengantarmu kesana.

1331
02:02:21,408 --> 02:02:23,533
Kau kira kau bisa membunuhku?

1332
02:02:24,200 --> 02:02:25,241
Jangan lupa,

1333
02:02:25,908 --> 02:02:28,283
semua yang kau pelajari,
aku yang ajarkan.

1334
02:02:28,575 --> 02:02:29,741
Selamatkan Ji Fa!

1335
02:02:48,200 --> 02:02:50,325
Nezha, Yang Jian, aku di sini!

1336
02:02:52,033 --> 02:02:52,908
Guru Ziya!

1337
02:02:54,200 --> 02:02:55,658
Ikutlah bersama kami!
Ay!

1338
02:02:55,783 --> 02:02:58,325
Jangan khawatirkan aku.
Bawalah Yin Jiao.

1339
02:02:58,700 --> 02:03:00,908
Yin Jiao sudah ada di dua alam!
Dia sudah mati.

1340
02:03:00,908 --> 02:03:01,825
Jangan buang waktu lagi!

1341
02:03:01,825 --> 02:03:04,158
Cepat bawa dia ke Kunlun!

1342
02:03:22,450 --> 02:03:23,325
Teleportasi Air!

1343
02:03:31,200 --> 02:03:32,366
Apa keduanya harus pergi?

1344
02:04:08,658 --> 02:04:10,325
Jika dewa tak mau membunuhmu,

1345
02:04:10,450 --> 02:04:12,025
aku yang akan membunuhmu.

1346
02:04:39,950 --> 02:04:41,658
Yang Mulia sudah mati.

1347
02:04:42,366 --> 02:04:45,991
Aku, Adipati Negeri Utara,
yang memerintah sekarang.

1348
02:05:07,033 --> 02:05:08,991
Bawakan aku Ji Fa.

1349
02:05:23,575 --> 02:05:24,991
Kenapa kau masih di Zhaoge?

1350
02:05:25,200 --> 02:05:26,366
Kau mau mati!

1351
02:05:37,408 --> 02:05:38,575
Pemindahan Roh!

1352
02:06:15,825 --> 02:06:17,241
Yin Shou sudah mati.

1353
02:06:17,700 --> 02:06:19,116
Aku membunuhnya.

1354
02:06:21,408 --> 02:06:23,783
Dialah yang bertanggung jawab
atas Kutukan Besar itu.

1355
02:06:24,075 --> 02:06:25,866
Hentikan mereka!

1356
02:06:34,075 --> 02:06:36,991
Jiang Wenhuan,
jika kau mau balaskan dendamnya,

1357
02:06:38,491 --> 02:06:39,950
balaskan sekarang.

1358
02:07:07,116 --> 02:07:08,283
Mundur!

1359
02:07:10,825 --> 02:07:12,125
Lepaskan mereka.

1360
02:07:18,033 --> 02:07:19,283
Pergi!

1361
02:07:29,700 --> 02:07:30,908
Tutup gerbangnya.

1362
02:07:31,033 --> 02:07:32,241
Bersiaplah berperang!

1363
02:07:57,783 --> 02:07:58,825
Ada yang datang!

1364
02:07:58,825 --> 02:07:59,866
Hentikan dia!

1365
02:08:05,241 --> 02:08:06,283
Hentikan dia sekarang!

1366
02:08:13,241 --> 02:08:14,033
Itu buronan.

1367
02:08:35,158 --> 02:08:36,658
Masuk ke hutan!

1368
02:08:38,200 --> 02:08:39,866
Ikuti aku!

1369
02:08:47,575 --> 02:08:48,866
Apa ini?

1370
02:09:18,241 --> 02:09:19,158
Panah!

1371
02:09:30,575 --> 02:09:32,533
Ji Fa, pergi.
Selamatkan dirimu.

1372
02:09:32,700 --> 02:09:34,533
Akulah yang mereka cari.

1373
02:09:36,325 --> 02:09:37,775
Aku pinjam dulu barangmu.

1374
02:09:37,783 --> 02:09:38,575
Apa?

1375
02:11:06,033 --> 02:11:09,283
Jangan buru-buru, Saudara Tao-ku.

1376
02:11:18,158 --> 02:11:19,783
Kau!

1377
02:12:43,200 --> 02:12:46,825
Jiang Ziya!
Kau takkan lolos!

1378
02:13:12,075 --> 02:13:13,658
Kau siapa?

1379
02:13:25,200 --> 02:13:26,950
Lei Zhenzi.

1380
02:13:34,950 --> 02:13:36,283
Anakku,

1381
02:13:37,825 --> 02:13:40,325
ayo kita pulang.

1382
02:14:23,950 --> 02:14:27,741
Kedua Naga Salju ini hadiah dari Ayah.

1383
02:14:28,033 --> 02:14:29,866
aku sudah melatihnya.

1384
02:14:30,741 --> 02:14:32,658
Kapan pun kau mau pulang,

1385
02:14:32,825 --> 02:14:34,700
katakan saja:

1386
02:14:34,950 --> 02:14:36,241
"Rumah".

1387
02:14:36,741 --> 02:14:38,408
Dan mereka akan mengantarmu
pulang ke Xiqi.

1388
02:14:48,075 --> 02:14:49,658
Kalung.

1389
02:14:53,908 --> 02:14:54,950
Ayah,

1390
02:14:56,241 --> 02:14:58,491
aku janji akan pulang ke Xiqi.

1391
02:15:05,700 --> 02:15:07,033
Kalung.

1392
02:15:12,491 --> 02:15:14,075
Kembali ke tempat asal.

1393
02:15:27,158 --> 02:15:28,991
Rumah.

1394
02:16:09,825 --> 02:16:11,200
Itu Naga Salju!

1395
02:16:11,366 --> 02:16:13,366
Tuan Muda pulang!

1396
02:16:29,825 --> 02:16:30,658
Ayah.

1397
02:16:56,825 --> 02:16:58,158
Ayo.

1398
02:17:08,991 --> 02:17:10,325
Kembali ke tempat asal.

1399
02:17:19,658 --> 02:17:20,700
Ayah,

1400
02:17:24,741 --> 02:17:26,491
aku kembali.

1401
02:24:59,741 --> 02:25:02,700
Panglima Shang Wen Zhong,

1402
02:25:02,700 --> 02:25:08,366
setelah 10 tahun berperang
di dekat Laut Utara,

1403
02:25:08,491 --> 02:25:12,325
dan pulang membawa kemenangan!

